<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-2542] Cron and Size Triggering Policies not rolling properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2542</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the Cron and SizeBased Triggering policies are used together they do not roll properly. When a size-based rollover occurs that starts just before the rollover time and ends just after the file name will use the next period&apos;s timestamp but increment the index to the next number when it should have a value of 1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
